939
01:10:53,581 --> 01:10:56,141
我能感觉到吹向你脸颊的海风
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I can feel the wind in your cheek.{\r}

940
01:11:02,924 --> 01:11:05,415
恐怕已经到午夜了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I'm afraid it's the witching hour.{\r}

941
01:11:11,332 --> 01:11:14,563
那是第一次有女人吻我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}It was the first time a woman had ever kissed me.{\r}

942
01:11:15,136 --> 01:11:17,536
难以忘怀
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}It's something you never forget.{\r}

943
01:11:28,049 --> 01:11:30,074
是你让我感觉年轻了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I think you make me feel younger.{\r}

944
01:11:30,184 --> 01:11:32,709
