946
01:11:35,423 --> 01:11:37,550
我会改变很多事
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}So many things I'd change.{\r}

947
01:11:38,259 --> 01:11:40,591
我会弥补所有的过错
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I'd undo all my mistakes.{\r}

948
01:11:40,695 --> 01:11:42,390
什么过错？
