{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Such an awful waste. You never get it back.{\r}

953
01:12:01,316 --> 01:12:02,783
人生就这么平白无辜地浪费了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Wasted time.{\r}

954
01:12:09,090 --> 01:12:11,490
如果我们在一起
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}If we're going to have an affair,{\r}

955
01:12:12,226 --> 01:12:15,059
白天千万不要见面
