{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}- Are you cold? - I'm freezing.{\r}

960
01:12:30,244 --> 01:12:32,178
哦 你！你快冻僵了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Oh, you! You're frozen.{\r}

961
01:12:32,280 --> 01:12:35,477
真傻 我还穿着皮衣呢 我怎么这么粗心
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}What an idiot, I'm standing here in this fur. How thoughtless of me.{\r}

962
01:13:09,150 --> 01:13:11,948
