963
01:13:14,922 --> 01:13:16,150
要我跳过一些内容吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}You want me to skip some?{\r}

964
01:13:16,257 --> 01:13:22,025
不用 我很高兴有人能温暖他
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}No, I'm glad he had somebody to keep him warm.{\r}

965
01:13:25,700 --> 01:13:28,168
“我等不及要再见到她”
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}"I couldn't wait to see her again."{\r}

966
01:13:41,082 --> 01:13:43,380
我们每晚见面
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}We saw each other every night.{\r}

967
01:13:43,985 --> 01:13:46,283
总是在同一间屋子
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}We always used the same room.{\r}

968
01:13:48,256 --> 01:13:51,589
可每次都有不同的体验
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}But each time seemed new and different.{\r}

969
01:13:52,994 --> 01:13:54,427
过来
