1426
01:56:20,150 --> 01:56:22,150
换了是你 也会这么做的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}You'd do the same for me.{\r}

1427
01:56:24,050 --> 01:56:25,250
我的天
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}My God.{\r}

1428
01:56:27,450 --> 01:56:30,850
瞧瞧你 你太完美了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Look at you. You're perfect.{\r}

1429
01:56:33,750 --> 01:56:38,250
