1438
01:57:11,950 --> 01:57:15,650
在纽约那会就想告诉你了 可你就是不听
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Tried to tell you that in New York. You don't listen.{\r}

1439
01:57:17,250 --> 01:57:19,150
你或许会改变主意
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}You might change your mind.{\r}

1440
01:57:19,250 --> 01:57:22,250
你也不是小孩子了 本杰明
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}We are not little children anymore, Benjamin.{\r}

1441
01:57:24,250 --> 01:57:27,450
拜托 从我的生命里消失吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Just stay out of my life.{\r}

1442
01:57:50,350 --> 01:57:53,550
我真的是太狠心了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I was awfully cruel.{\r}

1443
01:57:54,650 --> 01:58:00,050
他一定不明白 我只是不想让他看我那副样子
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}He didn't understand. I couldn't have him see me like that.{\r}

1444
01:58:02,750 --> 01:58:04,150
“我没有马上离开
