1446
01:58:13,750 --> 01:58:15,550
我一点也不知道
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I never knew that.{\r}

1447
01:58:18,950 --> 01:58:23,050
哦 亲爱的 能帮我叫下护士吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Oh, darling, could you get the nurse?{\r}

1448
01:58:26,750 --> 01:58:31,750
我又重新学会走路
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I taught myself to walk again.{\r}

1449
01:58:34,850 --> 01:58:37,350
