{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}All right, he says, "I went back home." And then there's a lot of pages torn out.{\r}

1454
01:59:08,050 --> 01:59:11,750
“我聆听着房子的低语” 我读过这段了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}"I listened to the sound of the house." I read that already.{\r}

1455
01:59:12,650 --> 01:59:13,750
他…
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}He...{\r}

1456
01:59:14,750 --> 01:59:17,950
他把什么东西溅到纸上 这段看不清了 妈
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}He spilt something on it, so it's hard to read, Mom.{\r}

1457
01:59:19,150 --> 01:59:21,850
好像是关于帆船的 您知道他在说什么吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Something about sailing, does that make sense?{\r}

1458
01:59:22,650 --> 01:59:26,050
