何必这么烦呢 山姆 反正明天还是要去一趟的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Don't know why you bother, Sam, just gonna be there again tomorrow.{\r}

1463
02:00:35,150 --> 02:00:36,250
妈妈
