1464
02:00:41,150 --> 02:00:43,550
1962年春天
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}And in the spring of 1962,{\r}

1465
02:00:47,450 --> 02:00:48,950
她回来了
