1482
02:03:57,250 --> 02:04:00,350
和你在一起的每分每秒 我都会珍惜
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I will enjoy each and every moment I have with you.{\r}

1483
02:04:05,550 --> 02:04:08,050
我跟你打赌 我在这能比你坚持更久
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I bet I can stay out here longer than you.{\r}

1484
02:04:08,150 --> 02:04:09,750
那我赌你撑不了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I bet you can't.{\r}

1485
02:04:12,550 --> 02:04:15,050
你脸上几乎没有皱纹
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Barely a line or a crease.{\r}

1486
02:04:15,550 --> 02:04:18,650
而我 每天都会多长出几条 不公平
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Every day I have more wrinkles. It's not fair.{\r}

1487
02:04:20,350 --> 02:04:24,050
我喜欢你的皱纹 每一条都爱
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I love your wrinkles. Both of them.{\r}

1488
02:04:29,750 --> 02:04:32,050
越活越年轻是种什么感觉？
