1489
02:04:34,550 --> 02:04:39,150
还真是很难形容 我自己又没法看到全部变化
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I can't really say. I'm always looking out my own eyes.{\r}

1490
02:04:44,150 --> 02:04:47,950
我要是成了黄脸婆 你还会爱我吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Will you still love me when my skin grows old and saggy?{\r}

1491
02:04:48,050 --> 02:04:52,550
