1495
02:05:17,650 --> 02:05:19,650
多可惜
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}And what a shame that is.{\r}

1496
02:05:22,650 --> 02:05:24,250
有些事情 是永恒的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Some things last.{\r}

1497
